{"tid":1903362,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"amd轉intel 換底板CPU 不需重裝win7方法","createTime":"2020-02-29T02:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T10:59:58.000Z","uid":69460,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"634da7c598337b92da53957aa9d5a6ebad6d065e","tid":1903362,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"2011年砌機<br />\n<br />\nAmd AMD Athlon II X2 250 cpu<br />\nMSi 870-g45 motherboard <br />\n2gb x 2 + 4gb = 8gb ram<br />\nAsus STRIX gtx960 2gb<br />\nWD blue 1 tb hdd<br />\nCooler master g550m 550w<br />\n<br />\n前排由hitachi 1tb clone去 wd blue 1tb <br />\n因為日立hdd老化個針頭跳軌short short地<br />\n<br />\nClone完用落正正常常但都慢慢地  <br />\n裝咗CSGO玩一陣部機熱熱地  重開機後睇片上下網無啦啦會突然自己reboot  之後突然黑屏 一時藍屏 <br />\n一時開到一時開唔到機 係指連bios入唔到 <br />\n一時cmos checksum bad <br />\n扙走電源 休息下 之後又開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經uninstall steam csgo <br />\nCPU 酒精清潔再吱上 Nt-h1 散熱膏<br />\n但都係無法預計不穩定地出現以上問題<br />\n應該係MB老化<br />\n<br />\n打算買二手i5 cpu z97 MB<br />\n其他全用舊<br />\n<br />\nWD 1TB 劃分 C盤200GB D盤800GB<br />\nC盤桌面有好多程式相片重要資料 回億<br />\n唔想重裝window <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爬好多文見其中係係將hdd sata由ahci 轉ide<br />\nwindow 隱藏軟件 sysprep可移除所有driver <br />\n可以直接攞hdd插去新硬件到直接用得 <br />\n類似重裝win7開個假使用者裝哂新driver 然後del個假使用者<br />\n裏面舊嘅程式仲係哂度<br />\n但唯一問題係桌面所有嘢唔見晒 會放落一個唔知咩File<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外方法一係用軟件back up window image落usb or dvd boot機 又ghost等 完全唔知咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知個個都叫重裝win7算啦乾淨簡單穩定搞咁撚多嘢做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但入面實在太多野同回億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋開機一陣會黑屏or reboot 唔可以操作太多嘢<br />\n<br />\n對電腦唔熟悉<br />\n有冇人教下用咩方法好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4dab407d240ba667b959aecbb7d2bfdb959964","tid":1903362,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:31:08.000Z","msg":"2011年砌咁嘅機<br />\n邊q個水你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d04e9b73315d9f0ba4a600fb476901204148cd","tid":1903362,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"btw 既然你clone得到<br />\n不如直頭Virtualize咗佢<br />\n砌新機然後當VM咁行舊機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ef470ce404acad7d80639ffe41a27508616bfc","tid":1903362,"uid":7045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"盤乜撚野"},{"pid":"70a069405079608963805d93a64e24a5ae4918c3","tid":1903362,"uid":282053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔將啲資料backup上cloud,之後砌過部新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e056d7104fb1e24bda75bee336f365552dd6c7be","tid":1903362,"uid":116289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"盤你老母"}]}